div.p:
Few counties, in proportion to their extent, contain so many gentlemen’s
                    seats as Flintshire. The most remarkable are, Mostyn Hall, Sir Thomas Mostyn;
                    Pengewern, Sir Edward Pryce Lloyd; Boddlewyddan, Sir John Williams; Kinmael
                    Hall, Reverend Edward Hughes; Gwernhailed, Philip Lloyd Fletcher, Esq.; Hamner
                    Hall, Sir Thomas Hanmer; Downing, David Pennant, Esq.; Halken, Earl Grosvenor;
                    Adwynt, J. Roberts, Esq.; Llewenny Hall, Lord Kirkwall.
